---
// Persönliche Vorstellung – Vertrauensaufbau durch echtes Gesicht
---

<section class="profil" aria-label="Über Irena">
  <div class="profil__inner animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="profil__image-col">
      <div class="profil__frame">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/profil-irena.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img
            src="/profil-irena.jpg"
            alt="Irena Woschkowiak, Inhaberin von Malatelier Auszeit in Gronau"
            class="profil__image"
            width="800"
            height="1064"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profil__text-col">
      <span class="profil__eyebrow">Deine Gastgeberin</span>
      <h2 class="profil__name">Irena Woschkowiak</h2>
      <div class="profil__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="profil__bio">
        Willkommen in meinem kleinen Atelier in Gronau! Bei mir findest du eine entspannte, kreative Auszeit vom Alltag.
        Ob allein, mit Freunden oder als Familie: ich zeige dir Schritt für Schritt, wie du dein eigenes Keramik-Unikat gestaltest.
      </p>
      <p class="profil__bio">
        Keine Vorkenntnisse nötig, nur gute Laune.
      </p>
      <p class="profil__closing">Ich freue mich auf dich.</p>
      <span class="profil__signature">Irena</span>
      <a href="#termin-buchen" class="profil__cta">Jetzt Termin buchen</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .profil {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) var(--gutter);
    background: var(--bg-paper, #FAF7F2);
  }

  .profil__inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }

  /* Bild-Spalte */
  .profil__image-col {
    position: relative;
  }

  .profil__frame {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 20px 60px rgba(66, 52, 48, 0.12),
      0 8px 20px rgba(66, 52, 48, 0.08);
  }

  .profil__frame::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .profil__image {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }

  .profil__frame:hover .profil__image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  /* Text-Spalte */
  .profil__text-col {
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  .profil__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-terra, #D96C4A);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .profil__name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Lora', serif);
    color: var(--brand-espresso, #423430);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .profil__divider {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent-terra, #D96C4A);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .profil__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-sans, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5D4E43);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .profil__closing {
    font-family: var(--font-sans, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5D4E43);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .profil__signature {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Lora', serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-sienna, #A0522D);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .profil__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-terra, #D96C4A);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-sans, 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(217, 108, 74, 0.3);
  }

  .profil__cta:hover {
    background: var(--brand-espresso, #423430);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(66, 52, 48, 0.25);
  }

  /* Tablet */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .profil__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 639px) {
    .profil__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .profil__image-col {
      max-width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .profil__frame {
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .profil__divider {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .profil__name {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
